(firstQuint)The Trusculpt (Radio Frequency) Device For Thigh Circumference Reduction.

 The primary efficacy variable for this study is the comparison of mean change in thigh circumference from baseline to 12 weeks between two arms.

 The primary research hypothesis is that the mean change in thigh circumference is 1 cm (indicating mean reduction).

